name: Calgary International Airport 2013 | An Aviation Music Video ᴴᴰ
description:
2013's been an amazing year of plane spotting at Calgary International Airport. I've discovered new spots, seen so many new planes, and met a lot of other spotters. This is also my 100th YYC plane spotting video. Let's see if I can get 100 more in 2014 ;)

Please note that this video is only a brief reflection on my spotting adventures in Calgary - I'll make a special video combining videos from the airports I've been to :)

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
_____________________________________________________

Check out my previous video: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bS12Ck1QBiM
(Norwegian 787 RTO)
